"<b>Undated</b>, un-dā′ted, <i>adj.</i> having no date.",
"<b>Undaunted</b>, un-dän′ted, <i>adj.</i> not daunted: bold: intrepid.—<i>adv.</i> <b>Undaun′tedly</b>, in an undaunted or bold manner.—<i>n.</i> <b>Undaun′tedness</b>, the state or quality of being undaunted or fearless: boldness.",
"<b>Undawning</b>, un-dawn′ing, <i>adj.</i> not yet dawning or showing light.",
