"<b>Underground</b>, un′dėr-grownd, <i>adj.</i> under the surface of the ground.—<i>n.</i> that which is underground.—<i>v.t.</i> to place underground.—<i>adv.</i> <b>Underground′</b>, beneath the surface of the earth.",
