"<b>Unipersonal</b>, ū-ni-pėr′son-al, <i>adj.</i> existing as only one person: (<i>gram.</i>) used in only one person.—<i>ns.</i> <b>Uniper′sonalist</b>; <b>Unipersonal′ity</b>.",
