"<b>Cain</b> (Heb.), artificer, smith.",
"<b>Caleb</b> (Heb.), a dog.",
"<b>Calvin</b> (L.), bald.—L. <i>Calvinus</i>, Fr. <i>Calvin</i>, <i>Cauvin</i>, Sp. <i>Calvo</i>.",
"<b>Camilla</b> (L.), an attendant at a sacrifice.—Fr. <i>Camille</i>.",
