"<b>Clara</b> (L.), bright.—Dim. <b>Clare</b>.—Fr. <i>Claire</i>, It. <i>Chiara</i>, Sp. <i>Clara</i>.",
"<b>Clarence</b> (L.), illustrious.",
"<b>Claribel</b> (L.), brightly fair.",
"<b>Clarice</b>, <b>Clarissa</b>, derivatives from <i>Clara</i>.",
"<b>Claud</b>, <b>Claudius</b> (L.), lame.",
"<b>Claudia</b>, fem. of <i>Claudius</i>.",
