"<b>Constant</b> (L.), firm, faithful.—L. <i>Constans</i>, <i>Constantius</i>, It. <i>Costante</i>, <i>Costanzo</i>, Sp. <i>Constancio</i>, Ger. <i>Constanz</i>.",
"<b>Constantine</b> (L.), firm.—L. <i>Constantinus</i>, It. <i>Costantino</i>, Sp. <i>Constantino</i>, Ger. <i>Constantin</i>.",
