"<b>Cuthbert</b> (A.S.), well-known splendour.",
"<b>Cynthia</b> (Gr.), of or from Mount Cynthus.",
"<b>Cyprian</b> (Gr.), of Cyprus.—L. <i>Cyprianus</i>.",
