"<b>Darius</b> (Pers.), preserver.",
"<b>David</b> (Heb.), beloved.—Dims. <b>Davy</b>, <b>Dave</b>.—Fr. <i>David</i>, It. <i>Davide</i>, <i>Davidde</i>, Ger. <i>David</i>.—Fem. <b>Davida</b>, <b>Vida</b>.",
"<b>Deborah</b> (Heb.), a bee.",
"<b>Delia</b> (Gr.), of Delos.",
