"<b>Eric</b> (A.S.), rich, powerful.—L. <i>Ericus</i>.",
"<b>Ernest</b> (Ger.), earnest.—Fr. <i>Ernest</i>, It. and Sp. <i>Ernesto</i>, Ger. <i>Ernst</i>.—Fem. <b>Ernestine</b>.",
