"</td>",
"</tr>",
"<tr>",
"<td>MEASURES OF WEIGHT.</td>",
"</tr>",
"<tr>",
"<td>The <b>GRAMME</b>, the unit of weight, is the <i>weight</i> of a cubic centimètre of distilled water at 4° Centigrade.</td>",
"</tr>",
"<tr>",
"<td>",
"<table>",
